{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Disallow fixed charges on fresh water and wastewater on water bill.",
        "additional_details": "Do not let the utility companies use the customers as their \"cash cow\". Customers should have value for money for the services provided where they are operated in a fair manner. Ban the practice of using fixed charges. We believe customers already pay the amount due and fixed charges are free income for the utility companies.",
        "background": "Many water companies have increased prices of supply without reinvestment in the system. Raw sewage has been pumped into the environment where the clean-up is again billed to customers as price increases. Bonuses and dividends should not come from such fixed or standing charges.",
